katex Plugin for DokuWiki

Enables katex (http://khan.github.io/KaTeX/) parsing of TeX math expressions in wiki pages

All documentation for this plugin can be found at
http://www.dokuwiki.org/plugin:katex

If you install this plugin manually, make sure it is installed in
lib/plugins/katex/ - if the folder is called different it
will not work!

Please refer to http://www.dokuwiki.org/plugins for additional info
on how to install plugins in DokuWiki.

### Syntax and Usage

Inline:

  <math>a^2 + b^2 = c^2</math>

Block:

  <math block>a^2 + b^2 = c^2</math>

在配置中可以修改katex的网址，katex显示比较弱，还在修改中，只能说基本够用了.主要是快。
